  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1c0e7f03fcf05b5e.jpg?v=1782535334\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7b-IMG_9333.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f3ae519f1d2a6803.jpg?v=1782535336\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7e-IMG_9342.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/40a4432a4fca13d9.jpg?v=1782535339\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7c-IMG_9334.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/46113624d8799e32.jpg?v=1782535342\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7f-IMG_9348.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d3e98427243cc7e8.jpg?v=1782535344\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7g-travnotebook.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/809074f14ffbd6d6.jpg?v=1782535347\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7d-IMG_9336.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f3503348213e9b8b.jpg?v=1782535350\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>photos by <a href=\"http://annmarieloves.com/\">Ann-Marie Espinoza</a></p><p>Ahh - the custom stamps I designed exclusively for <a href=\"http://www.papertales.com/store/p20/Amy_Tan_%26_Paper_Tales_Photopolymer_Stamp.html\">Paper Tales in San Diego</a> are back in stock. After tons of phone requests, they have made them available online <a href=\"http://www.papertales.com/store/p20/Amy_Tan_%26_Paper_Tales_Photopolymer_Stamp.html\">here</a>. Also it seems that my latest collection with American Crafts has been restocked in a lot of places. Find Better Together at scrapbook.com and Simon Says Stamp.</p>"
